      "bookmarkId": "814849_4_1142-1216",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1142-1216",
      "markText": "兵者，诡道也。故能而示之不能，用而示之不用，近而示之远，远而示之近。利而诱之，乱而取之，实而备之，强而避之，怒而挠之，卑而骄之，佚而劳之，亲而离之。",
      "totalCount": 4830,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1142&rangeEnd=1216",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1142&rangeEnd=1216"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_4_687-717",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "687-717",
      "markText": "道者，令民与上同意也，故可以与之死，可以与之生，而不畏危也。",
      "totalCount": 3104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=687&rangeEnd=717",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=687&rangeEnd=717"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_4_1398-1453",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1398-1453",
      "markText": "夫未战而庙算胜者，得算多也；未战而庙算不胜者，得算少也。多算胜，少算不胜，而况于无算乎！吾以此观之，胜负见矣。",
      "totalCount": 2607,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1398&rangeEnd=1453",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1398&rangeEnd=1453"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_5_547-612",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "547-612",
      "markText": "孙子曰：凡用兵之法，驰车千驷，革车千乘，带甲十万，千里馈粮。则内外之费，宾客之用，胶漆之材，车甲之奉，日费千金，然后十万之师举矣。",
      "totalCount": 2587,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=547&rangeEnd=612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=547&rangeEnd=612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_4_542-570",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "542-570",
      "markText": "孙子曰：兵者，国之大事，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。",
      "totalCount": 2540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=542&rangeEnd=570",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=542&rangeEnd=570"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_5_782-803",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "782-803",
      "markText": "故不尽知用兵之害者，则不能尽知用兵之利也。",
      "totalCount": 2400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=782&rangeEnd=803",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=782&rangeEnd=803"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_6_607-635",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "607-635",
      "markText": "是故百战百胜，非善之善者也；不战而屈人之兵，善之善者也。",
      "totalCount": 2210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=607&rangeEnd=635",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=607&rangeEnd=635"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_4_874-930",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "874-930",
      "markText": "故校之以计，而索其情。曰：主孰有道？将孰有能？天地孰得？法令孰行？兵众孰强？士卒孰练？赏罚孰明？吾以此知胜负矣。",
      "totalCount": 2032,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814849&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=874&rangeEnd=930",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f321405c6f01e7f51f077?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=874&rangeEnd=930"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814849_7_546-611",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "546-611",
